      • targetPotentialFields

        protected final java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,org.vadere.simulator.models.potential.fields.PotentialFieldAndInitializer> targetPotentialFields
        Stores all potential fields which represent the observation area. The key of the outer map equals the id of the floor, the key of the inner map equals the id of the target (there is a floor field per target).
